### FoodIT Menu Service - API Tests
### Use with VS Code REST Client or JetBrains HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

###
# Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###
# Get All Stores
GET {{baseUrl}}/stores

###
# Get a Specific Store
@store_id = 7ad9ef9a-8a40-408c-a491-e82cd851d060
GET {{baseUrl}}/stores/{{store_id}}

###
# Get Menu Items for a Store
GET {{baseUrl}}/stores/{{store_id}}/items
